/*! normalize.css v8.0.1 | MIT License | github.com/necolas/normalize.css */

/* Document
   ========================================================================== */

/**
 * 1. Correct the line height in all browsers.
 * 2. Prevent adjustments of font size after orientation changes in iOS.
 */

html 
  line-height: 1.15 /* 1 */
  -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100% /* 2 */


/* Sections
   ========================================================================== */

/**
 * Remove the margin in all browsers.
 */

body 
  margin: 0


/**
 * Render the `main` element consistently in IE.
 */

main 
  display: block


/**
 * Correct the font size and margin on `h1` elements within `section` and
 * `article` contexts in Chrome, Firefox, and Safari.
 */

h1 
  font-size: 2em
  margin: 0.67em 0


/* Grouping content
   ========================================================================== */

/**
 * 1. Add the correct box sizing in Firefox.
 * 2. Show the overflow in Edge and IE.
 */

hr 
  box-sizing: content-box /* 1 */
  height: 0 /* 1 */
  overflow: visible /* 2 */


/**
 * 1. Correct the inheritance and scaling of font size in all browsers.
 * 2. Correct the odd `em` font sizing in all browsers.
 */

pre 
  font-family: monospace, monospace /* 1 */
  font-size: 1em /* 2 */


/* Text-level semantics
   ========================================================================== */

/**
 * Remove the gray background on active links in IE 10.
 */

a 
  background-color: transparent


/**
 * 1. Remove the bottom border in Chrome 57-
 * 2. Add the correct text decoration in Chrome, Edge, IE, Opera, and Safari.
 */

abbr[title] 
  border-bottom: none /* 1 */
  text-decoration: underline /* 2 */
  text-decoration: underline dotted /* 2 */


/**
 * Add the correct font weight in Chrome, Edge, and Safari.
 */

b,
strong 
  font-weight: bolder


/**
 * 1. Correct the inheritance and scaling of font size in all browsers.
 * 2. Correct the odd `em` font sizing in all browsers.
 */

code,
kbd,
samp 
  font-family: monospace, monospace /* 1 */
  font-size: 1em /* 2 */


/**
 * Add the correct font size in all browsers.
 */

small 
  font-size: 80%


/**
 * Prevent `sub` and `sup` elements from affecting the line height in
 * all browsers.
 */

sub,
sup 
  font-size: 75%
  line-height: 0
  position: relative
  vertical-align: baseline


sub 
  bottom: -0.25em


sup 
  top: -0.5em


/* Embedded content
   ========================================================================== */

/**
 * Remove the border on images inside links in IE 10.
 */

img 
  border-style: none


/* Forms
   ========================================================================== */

/**
 * 1. Change the font styles in all browsers.
 * 2. Remove the margin in Firefox and Safari.
 */

button,
input,
optgroup,
select,
textarea 
  font-family: inherit /* 1 */
  font-size: 100% /* 1 */
  line-height: 1.15 /* 1 */
  margin: 0 /* 2 */


/**
 * Show the overflow in IE.
 * 1. Show the overflow in Edge.
 */

button,
input  /* 1 */
  overflow: visible


/**
 * Remove the inheritance of text transform in Edge, Firefox, and IE.
 * 1. Remove the inheritance of text transform in Firefox.
 */

button,
select  /* 1 */
  text-transform: none


/**
 * Correct the inability to style clickable types in iOS and Safari.
 */

button,
[type="button"],
[type="reset"],
[type="submit"] 
  -webkit-appearance: button


/**
 * Remove the inner border and padding in Firefox.
 */

button::-moz-focus-inner,
[type="button"]::-moz-focus-inner,
[type="reset"]::-moz-focus-inner,
[type="submit"]::-moz-focus-inner 
  border-style: none
  padding: 0


/**
 * Restore the focus styles unset by the previous rule.
 */

button:-moz-focusring,
[type="button"]:-moz-focusring,
[type="reset"]:-moz-focusring,
[type="submit"]:-moz-focusring 
  outline: 1px dotted ButtonText


/**
 * Correct the padding in Firefox.
 */

fieldset 
  padding: 0.35em 0.75em 0.625em


/**
 * 1. Correct the text wrapping in Edge and IE.
 * 2. Correct the color inheritance from `fieldset` elements in IE.
 * 3. Remove the padding so developers are not caught out when they zero out
 *    `fieldset` elements in all browsers.
 */

legend 
  box-sizing: border-box /* 1 */
  color: inherit /* 2 */
  display: table /* 1 */
  max-width: 100% /* 1 */
  padding: 0 /* 3 */
  white-space: normal /* 1 */


/**
 * Add the correct vertical alignment in Chrome, Firefox, and Opera.
 */

progress 
  vertical-align: baseline


/**
 * Remove the default vertical scrollbar in IE 10+.
 */

textarea 
  overflow: auto


/**
 * 1. Add the correct box sizing in IE 10.
 * 2. Remove the padding in IE 10.
 */

[type="checkbox"],
[type="radio"] 
  box-sizing: border-box /* 1 */
  padding: 0 /* 2 */


/**
 * Correct the cursor style of increment and decrement buttons in Chrome.
 */

[type="number"]::-webkit-inner-spin-button,
[type="number"]::-webkit-outer-spin-button 
  height: auto


/**
 * 1. Correct the odd appearance in Chrome and Safari.
 * 2. Correct the outline style in Safari.
 */

[type="search"] 
  -webkit-appearance: textfield /* 1 */
  outline-offset: -2px /* 2 */


/**
 * Remove the inner padding in Chrome and Safari on macOS.
 */

[type="search"]::-webkit-search-decoration 
  -webkit-appearance: none


/**
 * 1. Correct the inability to style clickable types in iOS and Safari.
 * 2. Change font properties to `inherit` in Safari.
 */

::-webkit-file-upload-button 
  -webkit-appearance: button /* 1 */
  font: inherit /* 2 */


/* Interactive
   ========================================================================== */

/*
 * Add the correct display in Edge, IE 10+, and Firefox.
 */

details 
  display: block


/*
 * Add the correct display in all browsers.
 */

summary 
  display: list-item


/* Misc
   ========================================================================== */

/**
 * Add the correct display in IE 10+.
 */

template 
  display: none


/**
 * Add the correct display in IE 10.
 */

[hidden] 
  display: none
sources.style\\_nav.sass:
.btn__menu
    font-size: 2rem
    z-index: 106
    
.bi-three-dots-vertical::before
    float: right
    z-index: 106
.nav
    width: 100vw
    z-index: 105
    height: 111px 
    transition: 0.5s
    top: 0px
    .nav__list
        transition: 0.5s
        gap: 40px
        &-item
            color: $light-inactive
            text-transform: uppercase
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif
            font-size: 14px
            letter-spacing: 2.5px
            position: relative
            white-space: nowrap            
.nav--mobile
    z-index: 105
    height: 100vh
    width: 100vw
    background: $menu-icons 
    transition: 0.5s
    top: 0px
    display: flex
    .nav__list
        transition: 0.5s
        .nav__list-item
            width: 60%
            color: $light-inactive
            text-transform: uppercase
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif
            font-size: 13px
            letter-spacing: 2px
            position: relative
            top: -25px
            display: flex !important
            &:nth-child(7)
                border: 1px white solid
                padding: 13px 45px
.menu__border
    width: 1300px
    height: 0px
    position: absolute
    bottom: 0px
    border-bottom: 1px solid #ffffff54
.dark
    background: $menu-icons
.dark_logo
    display: none
.dark .dark_logo 
    display: block
.dark .light_logo
    display: none

@media screen and (min-width: 992px) 
    .nav__list-item
        width: 15%
        &:nth-child(1)
            right: -50px
        &:nth-child(7)
            right: 40px
@media screen and (min-width: 1800px)
    .nav__list-item
        &:nth-child(1)
            right: -230px
            top: -16px
        &:nth-child(2)
            right: -134px
            top: -16px
        &:nth-child(3)
            right: 10px
            top: -16px
        &:nth-child(4)
            right: 14px
            top: -18px
        &:nth-child(5)
            right: 52px
            top: -16px
        &:nth-child(6)
            right: 225px
            top: -16px
        &:nth-child(7)
            top: -17px
            border: 1px white solid
            padding: 13px 45px
            right: 295px
            width: unset
sources.style\\_carousel.sass:
.carousel
    max-height: 900px
    max-width: 100vw
    overflow: hidden 
    &__container
        max-height: 900px
        width: 100vw
    &__item
        z-index: 2
        color: $light-inactive
        font-weight: 400
        text-align: center
    & p
        letter-spacing: 3.65px
        font-size: 12px
        margin-bottom: -40px
        text-transform: uppercase
    & h2
        font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif
        font-size: 50px
        position: relative
        top: 40px
    & button
        position: relative
        top: 40px
    &__img
        object-fit: none
        object-position: 50% 0%
        height: 100vh
        max-height: 900px
.thumbs
    z-index: 5
    gap: 10px
    .thumb
        position: relative
        top: -35px
        z-index: 5
        height: 5px
        width: 50px
        background: $light-inactive
        transition: 0.5s
        border-radius: 10px
        cursor: pointer
        &:hover
            opacity: 0.8
sources.style\\_article.sass:
.article-item

    & p.mb-0
        position: relative
        bottom: 17px
        font-size: 12px
        letter-spacing: 3.5px
        text-transform: uppercase
        color: $highlight-button
    & h2
        position: relative
        bottom: 10px
        letter-spacing: 0.90px !important
        margin-bottom: 20px !important
        line-height: 50px
    & p.pg
        position: relative
        bottom: -4px
        font-size: 15px
        letter-spacing: 0px !important
        line-height: 27px
        padding: 0px 10px 0px 0px
        color: $body-text
    & button
        position: relative
        bottom: -20px
sources.style\\_btn.sass:
.btn
    transition: 0.5s
    &--highlight
        background: $highlight-button
        color: $light-inactive
        height: 60px
        padding: 0px 58px
        font-size: 15px
        text-transform: uppercase
        letter-spacing: 3px
        filter: drop-shadow(0px 2px 10px #00000033)
        &:hover
            background: #C8A74B
            color:  $light-inactive
    &--dark
        background: #000000
        color: $light-inactive
        border: 1px solid $light-inactive
        &:hover
            background: $light-inactive
            color: #000000
            border: 1px solid #000000
sources.style\\_opinions.sass:
.opinions
    height: 100vh
    max-width: 100vw
    background: $light-inactive
    &__arrow-left
        position: relative
        bottom: 230px
    &__arrow-right
        position: relative
        bottom: 350px
    &__container
        margin: 0px 90px
        position: relative
        bottom: 52px
        min-height: 125%
        
        & header p
            position: relative
            color: $highlight-button
            bottom: -10px
            left: 1px
            letter-spacing: 2.45px
            text-transform: uppercase
            font-size: 14px
        & h3
            position: relative
            font-weight: 400
            bottom: -10px
            font-size: 32px
            letter-spacing: 0px
        & p
            position: relative
            font-weight: 400
            bottom: -60px
            line-height: 30px
            font-size: 17px
            letter-spacing: 0.5px
            padding: 0px 30px
            color: $body-text
        & small
            position: relative
            font-weight: 400
            bottom: -65px
            line-height: 30px
            font-size: 14px
            letter-spacing: 0.5px
            padding: 0px 30px
            color: $body-text
        & button
            position: relative
            font-weight: 400
            bottom: -95px
            

    &__article
        text-align: center

@media screen and (min-width: 767px)
    .opinions
        max-height: 125%
        &__arrow-left
            position: static
            bottom: 0px !important
        &__arrow-right
            position: static
            bottom: 0px !important
        & .btn
            padding: 10px

@media screen and (min-width: 992px)
    .opinions
        max-height: 600px
        & .btn
            padding: 0px 58px
sources.style\\_gallery.sass:
.gallery
    height: 100vh
    max-height: 100vh
    &__container
        margin: 37px 0px 40px 0px
        gap: 20px
    &__image
        transition: 0.5s
        cursor: pointer
        &:hover
            opacity: 0.9
.shadow__image
    transition: 0.5s
    position: fixed
    height: 100vh
    width: 100vw
    background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9019607843)
    display: block
    z-index: 998
@media screen and (min-width: 1368px)
    .gallery
        max-height: 673px !important
        position: relative
        &__image
            width: 200px !important
            height: 200px !important
        & h3 
            font-size: 34px
            position: relative
            font-weight: 400
            letter-spacing: -0.8px
        &__container
            position: relative
            bottom: 6px
        & .btn
            position: relative
            bottom: 6px
            padding: 0px 37px
@media screen and (min-width: 1951px)
    .gallery
        max-height: 673px !important
        position: relative
        &__image
            width: 310px !important
            height: 310px !important
sources.style\\_footer.sass:
.footer
    max-height: 100vh
    height: 100vh
    z-index: 106
    position: relative
    bottom: -4px
    &__img
        height: 100vh
        -o-object-fit: cover
        object-fit: cover
        -o-object-position: 50% 0%
        object-position: 50% 0%

    &__copyright
        color: $body-text
    &__container
        background: #000000e6
        
        & div.border-bottom
            max-width: 1300px
            opacity: 0.2
            border-bottom: 1px solid $body-text !important
@media screen and (min-width: 768px)
    .footer
        height: 495px !important
        &__list
            position: relative
            bottom: -5px
            &.about
                right: 13px
                letter-spacing: 0px    
            &.info
                left: 11px
                letter-spacing: 0px
            &.follow
                left: 22px
                letter-spacing: 0px
            &-title
                font-size: 24px
                font-weight: 400
                position: relative
                bottom: 3px
                
            & dd
                font-weight: 400
                text-transform: uppercase
                font-size: 13px
                letter-spacing: 3px
                line-height: 22px
                position: relative
                bottom: -3px
        & .social-media
            position: relative 
            gap: 15px !important
            bottom: -10px
        &__img
            height: 100%
            -o-object-fit: none
            object-fit: none
        small
            width: 500px
            position: relative
            bottom: 26px
            letter-spacing: -0.5px
            line-height: 26px
